stories.text:
Hey HN, does anyone know of a simple way to pull transactions from various US banks/credit cards? I know about Plaid but its not really usable for a single hacker. I have also seen tillermoney.com which connects with my banks however it only exports to a Google Sheet using some extension.

Anyone have any scripts/projects/APIs/resources that can help?
